      <title>尼日利亚央行称奈拉波动性已达最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-25/cardoso-says-nigeria-has-seen-worst-of-naira-volatility-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚央行行长奥拉耶米·卡多佐表示，央行对稳定奈拉所取得的进展“相对满意”，并认为过度波动可能已成为过去。他在伦敦接受彭博社詹妮弗·扎巴萨贾采访时发表了上述言论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-25/cardoso-says-nigeria-has-seen-worst-of-naira-volatility-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 11:21:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市暴跌后，法国基金经理寻求抵御危机的廉价资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/french-fund-managers-seek-crisis-proof-bargains-after-stock-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在经历了 2000 亿美元的损失后，法国股市看起来仍然脆弱，但一些投资者正在寻找能够承受选举相关风险的便宜货。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/french-fund-managers-seek-crisis-proof-bargains-after-stock-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 11:12:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡多佐：尼日利亚将尽一切努力控制通货膨胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-25/cardoso-vows-to-keep-nigeria-inflation-in-check-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚中央银行行长奥拉耶米·卡多佐表示，货币政策委员会“将尽一切努力确保通胀得到控制”。他在伦敦接受彭博社詹妮弗·扎巴萨贾采访时表示，货币政策委员会认为通胀是“尼日利亚未来的主要障碍”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-25/cardoso-vows-to-keep-nigeria-inflation-in-check-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 11:11:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>动量股仍有下跌空间：Academy 的 Tchir</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-25/room-to-downside-on-momentum-stocks-academy-s-tchir-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Academy Securities 宏观策略主管 Peter Tchir 表示，他通过大宗商品表达了对地缘政治风险的押注，并认为随着势头“开始减弱”，股市将出现回调。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-25/room-to-downside-on-momentum-stocks-academy-s-tchir-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 11:09:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着选举信心增强，对冲基金对英国持乐观态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/hedge-funds-are-bullish-on-the-uk-as-election-confidence-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对冲基金对英国越来越乐观，对英镑走强的押注升至九个月来最高水平，因为他们希望即将到来的选举能巩固英国向更稳定的中间派政策转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/hedge-funds-are-bullish-on-the-uk-as-election-confidence-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 11:04:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举恐慌开始消退，法国股市回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/french-bonds-hint-investor-nerves-are-calming-ahead-of-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国债券利差从十多年来的最高水平回落，表明投资者对周日提前举行的议会选举可能带来的混乱变得更加乐观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/french-bonds-hint-investor-nerves-are-calming-ahead-of-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 09:52:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
